metadata.name: Bored Abe Kayak Club #1
metadata.description: The Bored Abe Kayak Club is a collection of 777 unique Bored Abe NFTs, unique digital collectibles living on the Solana  blockchain. Your Bored Abe doubles as your Kayak Club membership card, and grants access to members-only benefits, this is a parody collection built in the likeness of our Abe. A NFT collection built by the community for the community. Visit www.BoredAbeKC.com for more details.
